  "description": {
   "en": "This manga adapts Hinamizawa Teiryūjo, the unreleased stage play that Ryukishi07 wrote and eventually transformed into the Higurashi no Naku Koro ni game/anime/live-action franchise.  \n  \nIn the recesses of the mountains… there's a bus stop at the outskirts of a village, called the \"Hinamizawa Bus Stop\". Rika, a female high-school student, together with her junior, Mion visit this place. Twisted relationships that are concerned with the dam construction in Hinamizawa, and the stories of the curse of \"Oyashiro-sama\" take root in this area. Is a tragedy waiting for them, or something else…?"
  },
